"match": 18}, {"center": 20, "mine": 12, "match": 19}, {"center": 16, "mine": 17, "match": 20}]};
const BASE_POS = [[28,26,44],[72,26,44],[50,50,40],[28,74,44],[72,74,44]];
const SAFETY = 2;
const hypot = (a,b)=>Math.hypot(a,b);
const clamp = (x,a,b)=>Math.max(a,Math.min(b,x));
function computeScale(posList){
  let s=1.0;
  for(const [x,y,sz] of posList){ const r=sz/2;
    s=Math.min(s,(x-SAFETY)/r,(100-x-SAFETY)/r,(y-SAFETY)/r,(100-y-SAFETY)/r); }
  for(let i=0;i<posList.length;i++){ for(let j=i+1;j<posList.length;j++){
    const [x1,y1,sz1]=posList[i],[x2,y2,sz2]=posList[j];
    const d=hypot(x2-x1,y2-y1), rsum=(sz1+sz2)/2; s=Math.min(s,(d-SAFETY)/rsum);
  }}
  return clamp(s,0.62,1.0);
}
function assignPositions(ids,pref){ const used=new Set(), out={};
  if(pref){ for(const sid of ids){ const p=pref[sid]; if(p!=null && !used.has(p)){ out[sid]=p; used.add(p);} } }
  for(const sid of ids){ if(out[sid]==null){ for(let i=0;i<BASE_POS.length;i++){ if(!used.has(i)){ out[sid]=i; used.add(i); break; } } } }
  return out;
}
function placeToken(cardEl,sid,posIdx,scale,clickable,onClick){
  const [x,y,sz0]=BASE_POS[posIdx]; const sz=sz0*scale;
  const t=document.createElement('button'); t.className='token';
  t.style.width=sz+'%'; t.style.height=sz+'%'; t.style.left=`calc(${x}% - ${sz/2}%)`; t.style.top=`calc(${y}% - ${sz/2}%)`;
  const sym=DECK.symbols.find(s=>s.id===sid);
  t.innerHTML=`<img alt="${sym.label}" src="${sym.img}">`;
  if(clickable) t.addEventListener('click', onClick);
  cardEl.appendChild(t); return t;
}

let isHost=false, room=null, roomRef=null;

const qs = (s)=>document.querySelector(s);

function code(){ const s='ABCDEFGHJKMNPQRSTUVWXYZ23456789'; let out=''; for(let i=0;i<5;i++) out+=s[Math.floor(Math.random()*s.length)]; return out; }

auth.signInAnonymously().then(cred=>{ uid=cred.user.uid; }).catch(console.error);

const lobby = document.getElementById('lobbyOverlay');

async function ensureUniqueName(baseName, roomPlayersRef){
  const snap = await roomPlayersRef.get();
  const players = snap.val()||{};
  const existing = new Set(Object.values(players).map(p=>p.name));
  if (!existing.has(baseName)) return baseName;
  let n=2;
  while (existing.has(`${baseName} (${n})`)) n++;
  return `${baseName} (${n})`;
}

document.getElementById('createRoom').addEventListener('click', async ()=>{
  const baseName=(qs('#playerName').value||'').trim(); if(!baseName) return alert('Digite seu nome');
  const img=avatarPrev.dataset.img||''; const emo=avatarPrev.dataset.emo||'üôÇ';
  const id = code();
  roomRef = db.ref('rooms/'+id);
  await roomRef.set({ createdAt: firebase.database.ServerValue.TIMESTAMP, host: uid, roundIdx: 0, rounds: DECK.rounds, scores: {}, state: 'playing' });
  const name = await ensureUniqueName(baseName, roomRef.child('players'));
  me = {name, avatar: img||emo, isEmoji: !img};
  await roomRef.child('players/'+uid).set(me);
  isHost=true; room=id; lobby.style.display='none';
  qs('#roomInfo').textContent='Sala: '+room; qs('#roleInfo').textContent='Host';
  qs('#playerHeader').textContent = 'Jogador ‚Äî ' + me.name;
  subscribeRoom(); renderRound();
});

document.getElementById('joinRoom').addEventListener('click', async ()=>{
  const baseName=(qs('#playerName').value||'').trim(); if(!baseName) return alert('Digite seu nome');
  const img=avatarPrev.dataset.img||''; const emo=avatarPrev.dataset.emo||'üôÇ';
  const id=(qs('#roomCode').value||'').trim().toUpperCase(); if(!id) return alert('Digite o c√≥digo da sala');

  const snap = await roomRef.get();
  if(!snap.exists()) return alert('Sala n√£o encontrada');
  const name = await ensureUniqueName(baseName, roomRef.child('players'));
  me = {name, avatar: img||emo, isEmoji: !img};
  await roomRef.child('players/'+uid).set(me);
  isHost=false; room=id; lobby.style.display='none';
  qs('#roomInfo').textContent='Sala: '+room; qs('#roleInfo').textContent='Jogador';
  qs('#playerHeader').textContent = 'Jogador ‚Äî ' + me.name;
  subscribeRoom(); renderRound();
});

function subscribeRoom(){
  roomRef.child('roundIdx').on('value', s=>{
    roundIdx = s.val()||0;
    qs('#rnum').textContent=String(roundIdx+1);
    clickedInRound = false;
    renderRound();
  });
  roomRef.child('scores').on('value', s=> { const sc=s.val()||{}; updateTop3(sc); maybeChampion(sc); });
  roomRef.child('roundWinners/'+roundIdx).on('value', s=> renderRoundRank(s.val()||{}));
  roomRef.child('showResults').on('value', s=>{ const v=s.val(); if(v&&typeof v.round==='number'){ showResultsModal(v.round); } else { hideResultsModal(); } }); if (!v) return;
    showResultsModal(v.round);
  });
}

function renderRound(){
  const r=DECK.rounds[roundIdx], center=DECK.cards[r.center], mine=DECK.cards[r.mine], common=r.match;
  const centerEl=document.getElementById('center'), mineEl=document.getElementById('mine');
  clear(centerEl); clear(mineEl);
  const mapCenter=assignPositions(center,null);
  const mapMine=assignPositions(mine, {[common]:(mapCenter[common]+1)%BASE_POS.length});
  const scaleCenter=computeScale(center.map(sid=>BASE_POS[mapCenter[sid]]));
  const scaleMine=computeScale(mine.map(sid=>BASE_POS[mapMine[sid]]));
  centerEls={}; mineEls={};
  center.forEach(sid=>centerEls[sid]=placeToken(centerEl,sid,mapCenter[sid],scaleCenter,false,null));
  mine.forEach(sid=>mineEls[sid]=placeToken(mineEl,sid,mapMine[sid],scaleMine,true,()=>{
    if (clickedInRound) return;
    clickedInRound = true;
    const guessesRef = roomRef.child('guesses/'+roundIdx+'/'+uid);
    guessesRef.transaction(cur => cur || true, (err, committed)=>{
      if (err || !committed) { return; }
      if (sid!==common) { return; }
      const winnerRef = roomRef.child('roundWinners/'+roundIdx+'/'+uid);
      winnerRef.transaction(cur => cur || {name: me.name, avatar: me.avatar, isEmoji: me.isEmoji, ts: firebase.database.ServerValue.TIMESTAMP},
        (wErr, wCommitted)=>{
          if (wErr || !wCommitted) return;
          roomRef.child('scores/'+uid).transaction(v => (v||0)+1);
          centerEls[sid]?.classList.add('is-match'); mineEls[sid]?.classList.add('is-match');
        });
    });
  }));
  roomRef.child('roundWinners/'+roundIdx).once('value').then(s=> renderRoundRank(s.val()||{}));
}

function updateTop3(scores){
  const playersRef = roomRef.child('players');
  playersRef.once('value').then(ps=>{
    const players = ps.val()||{};
    const arr = Object.keys(scores).map(uid=>({uid, name:(players[uid]?.name||'??'), avatar:(players[uid]?.avatar||'üôÇ'), pts:scores[uid]}));
    arr.sort((a,b)=>b.pts-a.pts);
    const top = document.getElementById('top3');
    top.innerHTML = '<div style="font-weight:800;">Principal geral:</div>';
    arr.slice(0,3).forEach((it,idx)=>{
      const badge = document.createElement('div');
      badge.className = 'badge';
      const avHTML = it.avatar.startsWith('data:image') ? `<img src="${it.avatar}">` : `<div class="emo">${it.avatar}</div>`;
      badge.innerHTML = `${avHTML}<span>${idx+1}¬∫ ${it.name} (${it.pts})</span>`;
      top.appendChild(badge);
    });
  });
}

function renderRoundRank(winnersObj){
  const el = document.getElementById('roundRank');
  el.innerHTML = '';
  const rows = Object.values(winnersObj||{});
  if (!rows.length){ el.innerHTML = '<span style="opacity:.7;">Aguardando acerto‚Ä¶</span>'; return; }
  rows.sort((a,b)=>(a.ts||0)-(b.ts||0));
  rows.forEach((w,i)=>{
    const pill=document.createElement('div');
    pill.className='rankpill';
    const avHTML = (w.avatar||'üôÇ').startsWith('data:image') ? `<img src="${w.avatar}" style="width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:50%;">` : `<span class="emo">${w.avatar||'üôÇ'}</span>`;
    pill.innerHTML = `${avHTML}<strong>${i+1}¬∫</strong> ${w.name}`;
    el.appendChild(pill);
  });
}

// ===== Resultados (mostrar ap√≥s host clicar Avan√ßar)
async function hideResultsModal(){ try{ document.getElementById('resultsOverlay').style.display='none'; }catch(e){} }
function showResultsModal(roundNumber){
  const overlay = document.getElementById('resultsOverlay');
  const listEl = document.getElementById('resultsList');
  const label = document.getElementById('resultsRoundLabel');
  label.textContent = 'Rodada ' + (roundNumber+1);

  const [playersSnap, winnersSnap] = await Promise.all([
    roomRef.child('players').get(),
    roomRef.child('roundWinners/'+roundNumber).get()
  ]);
  const players = playersSnap.val()||{};
  const winners = winnersSnap.val()||{};

  const winnersArr = Object.entries(winners).map(([uid,w])=>({uid, ...w})).sort((a,b)=>(a.ts||0)-(b.ts||0));
  const clickerUIDs = new Set(Object.keys(winners));

  const nonClickers = Object.entries(players)
    .filter(([k,v])=>!clickerUIDs.has(k))
    .map(([k,v])=>({uid:k, name:v.name, avatar:v.avatar, isEmoji:v.isEmoji}));

  listEl.innerHTML='';
  let idx=1;
  winnersArr.forEach(w=>{
    const div=document.createElement('div'); div.className='li';
    const avHTML = (w.avatar||'üôÇ').startsWith('data:image') ? `<img src="${w.avatar}" style="width:24px;height:24px;border-radius:50%;">` : `<span class="emo">${w.avatar||'üôÇ'}</span>`;
    div.innerHTML = `<div class="idx">${idx++}¬∫</div>${avHTML}<div class="name">${w.name}</div><div class="tag">acertou</div>`;
    listEl.appendChild(div);
  });
  nonClickers.forEach(nc=>{
    const div=document.createElement('div'); div.className='li missed';
    const avHTML = (nc.avatar||'üôÇ').startsWith('data:image') ? `<img src="${nc.avatar}" style="width:24px;height:24px;border-radius:50%;">` : `<span class="emo">${nc.avatar||'üôÇ'}</span>`;
    div.innerHTML = `<div class="idx">‚Äî</div>${avHTML}<div class="name">${nc.name}</div><div class="tag">n√£o clicou</div>`;
    listEl.appendChild(div);
  });

  // host controla o "Continuar"
  const btn = document.getElementById('continueBtn');
  btn.style.display = isHost ? 'inline-block' : 'none';
  overlay.style.display='flex';

  btn.onclick = async () => {
    // salva hist√≥rico desta rodada
    const hist = { winners: winnersArr, nonClickers: nonClickers, savedAt: firebase.database.ServerValue.TIMESTAMP };
    await roomRef.child('history/'+roundNumber).set(hist);
    // prepara pr√≥xima rodada: limpa guesses do round atual, esconde overlay e avan√ßa
    await roomRef.child('guesses/'+roundNumber).set(null);
    document.getElementById('resultsOverlay').style.display='none';
    // avan√ßa (ciclo infinito sobre 21 rounds, at√© algu√©m atingir 36 pts)
    await roomRef.child('roundIdx').transaction(v => ((v||0)+1) % DECK.rounds.length);
    // limpa flag de resultados
    await roomRef.child('showResults').set(null);
  };
}

document.getElementById('next').addEventListener('click', async ()=>{
  if (!isHost) return alert('Somente o host pode mostrar os resultados.');
  const current = roundIdx;
  await roomRef.child('showResults').set({ round: current, at: firebase.database.ServerValue.TIMESTAMP });
});

  await roomRef.child('showResults').set({ round: current, at: firebase.database.ServerValue.TIMESTAMP });
});

document.getElementById('resetScores').addEventListener('click', async ()=>{
  if (!isHost) return alert('Somente o host pode resetar.');
  if (!confirm('Zerar o ranking acumulado desta sala?')) return;
  await roomRef.child('scores').set({});
  await roomRef.child('roundWinners').set({});
  await roomRef.child('guesses').set({});
  await roomRef.child('showResults').set(null);
  await roomRef.child('history').set({});
});

// ===== Campe√£o (quando algu√©m alcan√ßa MAX_POINTS)
function maybeChampion(scores){
  const entries = Object.entries(scores||{}).map(([uid,pts])=>({uid, pts})).sort((a,b)=>b.pts-a.pts);
  if (!entries.length) return;
  if (entries[0].pts >= MAX_POINTS){
    // monta ranking final
    roomRef.child('players').once('value').then(ps=>{
      const players = ps.val()||{};
      const html = entries.map((e,i)=>{
        const name = players[e.uid]?.name || '??';
        const av = players[e.uid]?.avatar || 'üôÇ';
        const avHTML = av.startsWith('data:image') ? `<img src="${av}" style="width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:50%;vertical-align:middle;">` : `<span class="emo">${av}</span>`;
        return `<div class="li" style="margin:4px 0;"><div class="idx">${i+1}¬∫</div>${avHTML} <span class="name">${name}</span> ‚Äî ${e.pts} pts</div>`;
      }).join('');
      document.getElementById('champList').innerHTML = html;
      document.getElementById('champOverlay').style.display = 'flex';
    });
  }
}

// Reiniciar partida (mant√©m sala e jogadores)
document.getElementById('restartMatch').addEventListener('click', async ()=>{
  if (!isHost) return alert('Somente o host pode reiniciar a partida.');
  await roomRef.child('scores').set({});
  await roomRef.child('roundWinners').set({});
  await roomRef.child('guesses').set({});
  await roomRef.child('showResults').set(null);
  await roomRef.child('history').set({});
  await roomRef.child('roundIdx').set(0);
  document.getElementById('champOverlay').style.display = 'none';
});

// label inicial
document.getElementById('rnum').textContent='1';
